{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-139-pythagorean-tiles","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 139: Pitagorove noge","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Neka (a, b, c) predstavljaju tri stranice pravouglog trougla sa dužinama celobrojnim brojevima. Moguće je poređati četiri takva trougla zajedno kako bi se stvorio kvadrat sa stranicom dužine c.</p>\n<p>Na primer, trougaoci (3, 4, 5) mogu se poređati zajedno da formiraju kvadrat od 5 na 5 sa rupom od 1 na 1 u sredini, i čini se da se kvadrat od 5 na 5 može pokriti dvadeset pet pločica od 1 na 1.</p>\n<img alt=\"Dva kvadrata dimenzija 5 × 5: jedan sa četiri trougla dimenzija 3×4×5 raspoređena tako da formiraju otvor 1×1 u sredini; drugi sa dvadeset pet pločica dimenzija 1×1\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/pythagorean-tiles.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Međutim, ako se koriste trouglovi (5, 12, 13), rupa bi imala dimenzije 7 x 7. Kvadrat od 7 x 7 ne može se koristiti za pokrivanje kvadrata od 13 x 13.</p>\n<p>S obzirom na to da je stranica pravouglog trougla manja od miliona, koliko Pitagoreovih trouglova će omogućiti takvu pokrivenost?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3f71000cf542c50ff0a","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301767,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-139-pythagorean-tiles"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function pythagoreanTiles() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\npythagoreanTiles();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>pythagoreanTiles()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>10057761</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(pythagoreanTiles(), 10057761);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-101-to-200","dashedName":"problem-139-pythagorean-tiles","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":true,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-140-modified-fibonacci-golden-nuggets","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-138-special-isosceles-triangles","id":"5900f3f71000cf542c50ff0a","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-139-pythagorean-tiles"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}